 properly. This is the initial setup that will enable automated test coverage improvements.\n\n## Changes Made\n\nAdded `.github/actions/daily-test-improver/coverage-steps/action.yml` which provides a reusable GitHub Action that:\n\n1. **Restores dotnet tools** - Ensures AltCover and other build tools are available\n2. **Builds the solution** - Compiles FSharp.Stats in Release configuration\n3. **Runs tests with coverage** - Executes tests using AltCover to collect coverage data\n4. **Generates coverage report** - Creates `codeCov.xml` in Cobertura format\n5. **Uploads artifacts** - Makes coverage report and logs available for download\n\n## Technical Details\n\n### Coverage Configuration\n\nThe action uses AltCover (already configured in the test project) with these parameters:\n- `AltCover=true` - Enables coverage instrumentation\n- `AltCoverCobertura=../../codeCov.xml` - Outputs Cobertura XML format to repo root\n- `AltCoverForce=true` - Forces coverage generation even if previously run\n\n### Output Files\n\n- **codeCov.xml** - Cobertura format coverage report (placed in repository root)\n- **coverage-steps.log** - Detailed log of all build and test steps for debugging\n\n### Logging\n\nEach step appends its output to `coverage-steps.log` with clear section headers, making it easy to diagnose any issues that occur during the workflow.\n\n## Testing Recommendation\n\nPlease review this configuration carefully to ensure:\n\n1. The build and test commands match your project's needs\n2. The coverage report location is appropriate\n3. The logging approach works for your debugging workflow\n4. Any project-specific requirements are addressed\n\nThe next step after this PR is merged will be to manually test these steps to verify they work correctly in the CI environment.\n\n## Next Steps\n\nAfter merge, the Daily Test Coverage Improver will:\n1. Run these steps to generate coverage reports\n2. Analyze the coverage data to identify gaps\n3. Add meaningful tests to improve coverage\n4. Create pull requests with test improvements\n\n---\n\nðŸ¤– Generated with [Claude Code]((redacted))\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n\n\u003e AI generated by [Daily Test Coverage Improver](https://github.com/githubnext/gh-aw-trial-FSarpStats-claude/actions/runs/18593298544)","created_at":"2025-10-17T13:02:22Z","updated_at":"2025-10-17T13:02:34Z","closed_at":"2025-10-17T13:02:34Z","merged_at":"2025-10-17T13:02:33Z","user":{"login":"github-actions[bot]","id":41898282,"node_id":"MDM6Qm90NDE4OTgyODI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/15368?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/apps/github-actions","gravatar_id":"","type":"Bot","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/github-actions%5Bbot%5D/subscriptions"},"draft":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/githubnext/gh-aw-trial-FSarpStats-claude/pulls/3","html_url":"https://github.com/githubnext/gh-aw-trial-FSarpStats-claude/pull/3","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/githubnext/gh-aw-trial-FSarpStats-claude/issues/3","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/githubnext/gh-aw-trial-FSarpStats-claude/statuses/4b74fa6a8ccfedb37399a75f09131f3e04355c62","diff_url":"https://github.com/githubnext/g